---

### ğŸ“ Chapter 3 Summary

**Key Takeaways:**
- âœ… ADM is iterative and flexible, not a rigid waterfall process
- âœ… You can iterate within phases, across phases, and across full ADM cycles
- âœ… ADM scope can be tailored (focus on specific architecture domains)
- âœ… Every organization should tailor TOGAF to their context
- âœ… Requirements Management is the thread that runs through all phases

